---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Processo de Reconhecimento | Instituto Saber Global" currentPage="reconhecimento">

<!-- Section 1: Hero -->
<section class="relative pt-24 pb-16 md:pt-48 md:pb-32 px-6 overflow-hidden bg-surface">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-10 lg:gap-16">
    <div class="flex-1 lg:pr-8 z-10 text-center lg:text-left">
      <span data-animate="fade-right" class="inline-block text-tertiary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-4">
        PROCESSO DE EQUIVALÊNCIA
      </span>
      <h1 data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 100ms;" class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-on-surface tracking-tighter leading-[1.1] mb-8">
        Reconhecimento de Diplomas <span class="text-primary italic">Estrangeiros</span>
      </h1>
      <div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 200ms;" class="text-base sm:text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed max-w-xl space-y-4 mb-8 text-center md:text-justify mx-auto lg:mx-0">
        <p>O Instituto Saber Global preza pela transparência e conformidade com as normas educacionais brasileiras. Ao cursar um Mestrado ou Doutorado internacional, o aluno deve estar ciente de que, para ter validade plena no Brasil, o título deve passar pelo processo de reconhecimento.</p>
        <p>Este procedimento é regido pelo Decreto nº 9.235/2017 e pela Resolução CNE/CES nº 1/2022.</p>
      </div>
      <div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 400ms;" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4">
        <a href="/contato" class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-green-500/30 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 active:scale-95 cursor-pointer">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">support_agent</span>
          Falar com Especialista
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 relative w-full" data-animate="zoom-in" style="transition-delay: 300ms;">
      <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-64 h-64 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="relative rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden perspective-img shadow-2xl shadow-primary/20 aspect-square">
        <img alt="Diploma e credenciais acadêmicas" class="w-full h-full object-cover bg-surface-container-lowest" src="/images/reconhecimento.png" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/30 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 2: Revalidação vs Reconhecimento -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6 bg-primary text-on-primary relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-[-20%] left-[-10%] w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[#1ca1ff] opacity-10 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse pointer-events-none" style="animation-duration: 6s;"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-[-20%] right-[-10%] w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[#42a8f5] opacity-20 rounded-full blur-[150px] animate-pulse pointer-events-none" style="animation-duration: 9s;"></div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-20 relative z-10">
    <div class="mb-12 md:mb-16 text-center" data-animate="fade-up">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight mb-4 text-white">O que é o Reconhecimento?</h2>
      <div class="h-1.5 w-24 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6" style="background-color: #f5a623;"></div>
      <p class="text-blue-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">Diferente da graduação (que passa por revalidação), os títulos de pós-graduação stricto sensu (Mestrado e Doutorado) passam pelo processo de reconhecimento.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 200ms;" class="bg-[#185880] p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-black/30 group border border-transparent cursor-default">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center sm:items-start gap-8">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary-fixed rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary transition-colors shrink-0">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary-fixed group-hover:text-white transition-colors text-4xl">verified</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed text-lg text-justify font-medium pt-2">
            Este trâmite é realizado por universidades brasileiras (públicas ou privadas) que possuam cursos avaliados pela CAPES na mesma área de conhecimento e em nível igual ou superior.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 3: Plataforma Carolina Bori -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto overflow-hidden">
  <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-10 lg:gap-24">
    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative" data-animate="fade-right">
      <div class="relative rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden perspective-img shadow-2xl shadow-primary/20 aspect-[4/3]">
        <img alt="Interface da Plataforma Carolina Bori" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover bg-surface-container-lowest" src="/images/carolina-bori-reconheicmento.png" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/30 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 space-y-8 md:space-y-10 text-center lg:text-left" data-animate="fade-left">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter text-on-surface mb-6">Centralização e Agilidade</h2>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed text-center md:text-justify">
          O processo de reconhecimento é feito de forma digital através da Plataforma Carolina Bori, o sistema oficial do Ministério da Educação (MEC).
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-surface-container-lowest transition-colors border border-transparent hover:border-outline-variant/10 hover:shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary-fixed flex items-center justify-center text-on-primary-fixed font-black text-xl">1</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-on-surface text-xl">Transparência</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant mt-1">O aluno pode acompanhar todas as etapas do processo online.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-surface-container-lowest transition-colors border border-transparent hover:border-outline-variant/10 hover:shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-secondary-fixed flex items-center justify-center text-on-secondary-fixed font-black text-xl">2</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-on-surface text-xl">Padronização</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant mt-1">A plataforma reúne as normas e os procedimentos para que o trâmite ocorra com isonomia e clareza.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-surface-container-lowest transition-colors border border-transparent hover:border-outline-variant/10 hover:shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-tertiary-fixed flex items-center justify-center text-on-tertiary-fixed font-black text-xl">3</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-on-surface text-xl">Critérios</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant mt-1">A análise foca na equivalência acadêmica, mérito e qualidade da tese ou dissertação defendida.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 4: O Papel do Instituto -->
<section class="bg-surface-container-low py-16 md:py-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 md:mb-16" data-animate="fade-up">
    <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase rounded-full mb-6">Expertise Institucional</span>
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mt-4 mb-6 tracking-tighter text-on-surface">Assessoria e Suporte Documental</h2>
    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Para facilitar essa jornada, o Instituto Saber Global oferece suporte especializado aos seus alunos em todos os passos.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 100ms;" class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 rounded-3xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-[0.98] cursor-pointer hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-on-surface/5 group border border-transparent text-center flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary-fixed rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-on-primary-fixed mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">description</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 text-on-surface">Orientação Documental</h3>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/10 pt-4 w-full">Auxílio na organização dos históricos, diplomas e ementas conforme exigido pelas universidades brasileiras.</p>
    </div>
    <div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 250ms;" class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 rounded-3xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-[0.98] cursor-pointer hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-on-surface/5 group border border-transparent text-center flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-secondary-fixed rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-on-secondary-fixed mb-8 group-hover:bg-secondary group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">public</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 text-on-surface">Trâmites no Exterior</h3>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/10 pt-4 w-full">Orientação sobre o apostilamento de Haia e legalizações necessárias no país de origem (Paraguai/UNADES).</p>
    </div>
    <div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 400ms;" class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 rounded-3xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-[0.98] cursor-pointer hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-on-surface/5 group border border-transparent text-center flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-tertiary-fixed rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-on-tertiary-fixed mb-8 group-hover:bg-tertiary group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">school</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 text-on-surface">Consultoria Educativa</h3>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/10 pt-4 w-full">Explicação detalhada sobre os acordos de admissão de títulos no âmbito do Mercosul.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 5: Acordos MERCOSUL -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
  <div data-animate="zoom-in" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#185880] to-primary shadow-2xl shadow-[#185880]/30 p-4 md:p-6 rounded-[2rem] flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-0 items-stretch overflow-hidden text-on-primary border border-white/10 text-center md:text-left">
    <div class="md:w-5/12 relative rounded-[1.5rem] overflow-hidden perspective-img shadow-2xl shadow-primary/20 min-h-[250px] md:min-h-[300px]">
      <img alt="Acordos Mercosul" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover bg-surface-container-lowest" src="/images/mercosul-reconhecimento.png" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/30 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-7/12 p-4 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-4 md:mb-6 text-white drop-shadow-sm">Acordos MERCOSUL</h2>
      <p class="text-blue-100 font-medium text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed md:text-justify mb-4 drop-shadow-sm">
        Os cursos oferecidos pela Universidad Del Sol (UNADES) seguem os protocolos de integração educacional do Mercosul.
      </p>
      <p class="text-blue-100 font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed text-justify drop-shadow-sm">
        Embora os acordos facilitem a admissão para fins de estudo e pesquisa, o reconhecimento para fins profissionais e de exercício de magistério segue a legislação específica do MEC rigorosamente.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA Final -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-surface-container-low text-center px-6">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto" data-animate="zoom-in">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-6 text-on-surface">Pronto para validar sua trajetória?</h2>
    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-base md:text-lg mb-10">Tire suas dúvidas sobre a validade do seu título com nossa equipe jurídica e acadêmica.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="/contato" class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 text-white px-8 md:px-10 py-4 md:py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-green-500/30 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">support_agent</span>
        Falar com Especialista
      </a>
      <a href="/contato" class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 md:px-10 py-4 md:py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-blue-700 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-blue-600/30 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">public</span>
        Guia Carolina Bori
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- [SCROLL ANIMATIONS SCRIPT & STYLES] -->
<style is:global>
  /* Base animation setup */
  [data-animate] {
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }
  
  /* Reset hover duration speed */
  [data-animate]:hover {
    transition-duration: 150ms !important;
  }
  
  /* Initial states */
  [data-animate="fade-up"] { transform: translateY(40px); }
  [data-animate="fade-right"] { transform: translateX(-40px); }
  [data-animate="fade-left"] { transform: translateX(40px); }
  [data-animate="zoom-in"] { transform: scale(0.93); }
  
  /* Visible state */
  [data-animate].is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: none;
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Setup intersection observer on page load
  function initAnimations() {
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('is-visible');
          // Unobserve to run the animation only once
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, { 
      threshold: 0.15, // Trigger when 15% visible
      rootMargin: "0px 0px -50px 0px" // Trigger slightly before it hits bottom of viewport
    });

    document.querySelectorAll('[data-animate]').forEach((el) => {
      observer.observe(el);
    });
  }

  // Run immediately
  initAnimations();
</script>

</Base>
